{"tid":1109682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廉署九巴極速抽水 「咪以為保密到足 就可以Cheating」","createTime":"2019-04-16T10:44:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T12:16:19.000Z","uid":3090,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"abf57102bee2483b567aa9f1ae9dbb02cf736ae1","tid":1109682,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:44:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L2DqahA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL2DqahA.png&h=142a0d43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《蘋果》製圖、右圖取自廉署和九巴facebook<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UmdxzKm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmdxzKm.png&h=5ba37a36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九巴facebook圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LHHqUKt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLHHqUKt.png&h=86c29b5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廉署facebook圖片<br />\n<br />\n歌手許志安與家住鯉魚門的藝人黃心穎，被拍下在車內「偷食」片段。廉政公署的facebook專頁「全城‧傳誠」，極速以《Cheat精Cheating斷到正》為題發帖「抽水」，呼籲網民「咪以為保密工夫做到足，就可以Cheating；數碼足迹、天眼到處都係」、「咪以為黑蚊蚊冇人知，做過梗有痕迹」、「#教而不善 #收授雙方一齊玩完 #貪心邊有得咁安心 #要學識制服心魔同誘惑 #現實離奇過劇集」，可謂語帶雙關。九巴亦以《偷食至係罪大惡極！》為題出post，寸爆二人「偷食」：「#車廂唔畀食嘢是常識吧」、「#鯉魚門線呢期會睇緊啲」。<br />\n<br />\n廉署抽水全文<br />\n<br />\n【Cheat精Cheating斷到正】咪以為保密工夫做到足就可以Cheating，數碼足迹、天眼到處都係，要搵貪污證據，其實唔難，邊有咁易走得甩？<br />\n<br />\n#正Cheat精 #Cheating #人太貪婪心盲無明 #貪念是一條大坑會坑掉人的哦 #SoSad #教而不善 #收授雙方一齊玩完 #貪心邊有得咁安心 #要學識制服心魔同誘惑 #現實離奇過劇集 #全城傳誠 #AllforIntegrity #ICAC<br />\n<br />\n九巴抽水全文<br />\n<br />\n【偷食至係罪大惡極！】<br />\n你知唔知道其實巴士上面都有Cam㗎！如果你喺車上偷偷哋食嘢一樣會被發現！到時被人瘋傳就唔好啦！另一半見到點算好呢<br />\n<br />\n#KMB #九巴 #偷食係唔啱㗎 #車廂唔畀食嘢是常識吧 #若要人不知 #唔好太低B #鯉魚門線呢期會睇緊啲 #我哋巴士冇老鼠㗎 #大家可以安心搭九巴"},{"pid":"d6b0dfe1804fb80f2e6abc434cc90e237d7daba7","tid":1109682,"uid":143078,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:46:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n查689又唔見咁快手"},{"pid":"f100f61a91aa3f9006cf01d00d1a0669e6c09d4a","tid":1109682,"uid":68556,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:55:57.000Z","msg":"創意無限  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"409938d672a88a1e4e746d2a1ba15ab303c08fb6","tid":1109682,"uid":22337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T11:44:20.000Z","msg":"屌你 周不時搭14x<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d7de62480899979ed870986dc27954f58b0b820","tid":1109682,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T12:11:47.000Z","msg":"廉署用小畫家出圖？"},{"pid":"d74087d1ea5c93fb9f4dcca88c4d11b258e2c40b","tid":1109682,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d7de62480899979ed870986dc27954f58b0b820","tid":1109682,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T12:11:47.000Z","msg":"廉署用小畫家出圖？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T12:14:04.000Z","msg":"睇真啲啲頭髮<br />\n成堆X毛咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再睇隻嘢個顏色<br />\n我屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a55c70118ed1b516aa48d4bd7eda580163dc822f","tid":1109682,"uid":76745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T12:14:05.000Z","msg":"廉署果隻鳩毛怪想表達乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5949f5a74ec4e6e3520fb22b035a91430c4c862e","tid":1109682,"uid":73536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T12:16:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}